comments: This class is boring and straight forward. That being said, it is a decent way to complete requirements or get a QR credit.

depends on what the student wants. This class is good for some students who have never seen calculus before and enjoy a relatively slow pace.

Hard if you havent done AP calc, you need to teach yourself with the book and not think it is an easy class because the Yale Math department is ridiculously weird and difficult.I wouldn't recommend it, unless you get a really good professor/TA
